Please explain how I install it. I double clicked on "Deep Rybka 4 SSE42 w32.exe" and nothing happened. I double clicked on "Deep Rybka 4 w32.exe" and a blank command box-- nothing else. Please help; thank you.

CubanNuke you must install using a Graphic User Interface (GUI) that accepts UCI chess engines. For example Shredder UCI, Fritz/Junior/Shredder/Hiarcs, Arena, Aquarium, Chessbase, Chess Assistant, Chess Partner, or Tarrasch. Each GUI comes with its own instructions re how to install UCI engines.
